---
title: Chickpea-Powered Mediterranean Couscous with Roasted Veggies and Goat Cheese
description: Simple Mediterranean flavours come together in the most blissful way in this dish. Fresh and light veggies, couscous and chickpeas fill you up without a heavy feeling. Add ultra creamy goat cheese and you have a winner!
